"Summary": "West Liberty Foods is a protein processing company headquartered in West Liberty, Iowa. With facilities in Iowa, Illinois, and Utah, the company produces various meat and poultry products for major grocery chains and restaurants. West Liberty Foods is known as “The Surprisingly Big Company” due to its significant production capacity of over 650 million pounds of food annually. The company emphasizes its family-oriented atmosphere and commitment to environmental responsibility.",
